<extend name="Base/common"/>
<block name="style">
    <link href="__CSS__/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</block>
<block name="body">
    <div class="wrap">
        <empty name="orderData">
            <div class="check-info">
                <p class="check-info-p">您当前没有可用的门票，请购买。</p>
                <a href="{:U('index/activity')}" class="pay-btn">购买门票</a>
            </div>
        <else />
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">通过此手机购买的门票</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="tit">购票手机 {$info.mobile}</div>
                    <img width="138" height="138" src="__ROOT__/{$codeImgUrl}">
                    <ul class="describe">
                        <li>1. 请妥善保存该门票二维码，凭二维码可兑换纸质门票</li>
                        <li>2. 在园内哥特广场指定点换取小礼品一份, 并参与现场抽奖</li>
                        <li>3. 如若丢失，可在公众号“成都樱花节”下点击“门票查询”</li>
                        <li>4. 如有疑问，请致电客服400-019-7090</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <p class="tit">此二维码包含门票信息包含：</p>
                    <div class="cardinfo">

                        <notempty name="info.normalYesCount">
                        <div class="mincard-wrap">
                            <img width="23" height="35" src="__IMG__/ticket11.png"></img>
                            <span class="desc">
                                <span class="top">{$info.normalYesCount}<span class="sub">张</span></span>
                            <span class="bottom">未兑换</span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        </notempty>

                        <notempty name="info.yyYesCount">
                            <div class="mincard-wrap">
                                <img width="23" height="35" src="__IMG__/ticket12.png"></img>
                            <span class="desc">
                                <span class="top">{$info.yyYesCount}<span class="sub">张</span></span>
                            <span class="bottom">未兑换</span>
                            </span>
                            </div>
                        </notempty>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btlink">
                <a class="active" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODM1Njk4OA==&amp;mid=405350758&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a21b58147eb67f5cadbb983be64179b1#rd">查看攻略</a>
                <a href="{:U('map/index')}">查看地图</a>
                <a href="{:U('index/activity')}">继续购票</a>
            </div>
        </empty>
    </div>
</block>